  "Solve the logistic equation dP/dt = 0.5P(1 - P/100) with P(0) = 10 to find A in P(t) = 100/(1 + Ae^(-0.5t)).": "以P(0)=10在P(t)=100/(1+Ae(-0.5t)中找到A,解决后勤方程式dP/dt=0.5P(1-P/100)",
