  "The logistic equation dP/dt = 0.3P(1 - P/600) has solution P(t) = 600/(1 + Be^(-0.3t)). If P(0) = 200, find B and P(10).": "后勤方程式dP/dt = 0.3P(1 - P/600) 的溶液P(t) = 600/(1 + Be(-0.3t).如果P(0) = 200,请找到B和P(10))。",
